---
title: "US23 — Create / like / comment on posts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>SocialScreen / PostDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>TogglePostLike / AddPostComment
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Post · PostLike · PostComment
  A->>B: tap like
  B->>C: toggle(postId)
  C->>E: togglePostLike(postId)
  E-->>C: PostLike (added/removed) + like count
  A->>B: write a comment, tap Post
  B->>C: addComment(postId, body)
  C->>E: addPostComment(postId, body)
  E-->>C: PostComment + comment count
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (updated counts)
  B-->>A: like + comment reflected
  note over E: togglePostLike / addPostComment via SocialGateway → post_likes · post_comments (RLS) [planned]
